    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You weave illusion magic into your arrow, causing it to occlude your foe's vision with shadows. The creature hit by the arrow takes a number of additional d6 equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of 1) extra psychic damage, and it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be unable to see anything farther than 5 feet away until the start of your next turn.</p><p>After you reach 15th level in this class, the effect lasts up to 1 minute. The creature can make a Wisdom saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p>",
